{
  "stem": "24364.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the-- the opportunity arose so that I could really enter nurse's training, they gave us a-- gave us a-- a special arrangement had been made for some of the female soldiers in the war, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who had, you know, served during the war and who wanted to become nurses.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they made the training, which normally lasted three years, they made it into two years, and they accepted a couple of us to this particular training.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had to study Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We studied Hebrew like crazy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to pass an exam, which I passed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I didn't pass the physical, because of my knee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So after that happened, I stayed in Israel for-- in Palestine for about a year and a half.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And during that time, I had 17 jobs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I worked as a clerk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My English was pretty good at that time already, and I worked as a clerk in one of the military hospitals.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I worked as clerk in one of the military camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I worked as a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not as a-- helper in a restaurant, or in two restaurant.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I worked for a little factory, which made lipsticks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what else I did, but I constantly changed jobs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I really didn't know what to do with myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then finally, I-- there was a course for social workers, which I decided I might take.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had really great difficulties with the language.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was working very hard and I didn't have enough money and it was very unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the meantime, I had-- I had an aunt in my hometown who was in a mixed marriage.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
